00:42:46,137 --> 00:42:49,580
just make sure that they're supporting a goal

916
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:51,201
that the game has, right?

917
00:42:51,321 --> 00:42:53,023
That that is ultimately what you're trying to do

918
00:42:53,063 --> 00:42:54,304
with your character at all times,

919
00:42:55,024 --> 00:42:57,846
is make it reflect the gameplay intentions

920
00:42:58,647 --> 00:42:59,628
that the game has itself.

