933
00:43:46,228 --> 00:43:47,709
So if I'm on an interactive sequence,

934
00:43:47,749 --> 00:43:51,970
and my character's life depends on my actions,

935
00:43:52,190 --> 00:43:54,930
and if I don't perform those actions correctly,

936
00:43:55,371 --> 00:43:56,911
there has to be a consequence that makes me go,

937
00:43:57,051 --> 00:43:59,492
oh, I better not do that again, I better do that better.

938
00:43:59,912 --> 00:44:01,532
