00:44:25,728 --> 00:44:27,849
for the treacherous situations that you're in.

949
00:44:28,530 --> 00:44:30,892
So as the character progressed,

950
00:44:30,952 --> 00:44:32,093
like in Rise of the Tomb Raider,

951
00:44:32,554 --> 00:44:33,915
we still had our brutal deaths,

952
00:44:33,955 --> 00:44:36,497
but there weren't as many, and they weren't as frequent,

953
00:44:36,958 --> 00:44:38,839
and that wasn't because we were trying to be more PC.

954
00:44:39,180 --> 00:44:41,181
We were really trying to say that the character's grown,

955
00:44:41,722 --> 00:44:43,784
and that her competence has improved.

