00:45:29,806 --> 00:45:31,307
So we really couldn't design the character

975
00:45:31,327 --> 00:45:32,068
without having that.

976
00:45:32,168 --> 00:45:34,630
Now, when it came to that story that I went through,

977
00:45:34,770 --> 00:45:36,631
that whole loop of how Lara went through

